President Muhammadu Buhari has heartily congratulated Vice-President Yemi Osinbajo on the occasion of his 63rd birthday anniversary. A statement issued in Abuja on Sunday by Garba Shehu, Senior Special Assistant to the President (Media & Publicity), said in a telephone call Sunday afternoon to his vice, the President commended Osinbajo’s loyalty and dedication to the administration. ALSO READ: Osinbajo at 63: You have shown exceptional loyalty in government ― Lawan Rights group demands amnesty for inmates in correctional… Why bandits are killing people ― Buhari Nigeria wastes millions of dollars annually on barite… FG to adopt tech for increased farm yields ― Buhari President Buhari noted that the intellectual capacity of the Vice-President has impacted positively on the overall accomplishments of Federal Government, most notably, in the economic and social intervention programmes. The President joined family members, friends and associates of Prof. Osinbajo in wishing him joyous birthday celebration. He also prayed Almighty God to endow the Vice-President with greater wisdom and long life to continue to serve the nation and humanity. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! HERE IS HOW OVER 5000  NIGERIA MEN HAVE PERMANENTLY OVERCOME TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS RECENT DISCOVERY BY MEDICAL CONSULTANTS LOOK!  YOU DONT NEED TO HAVE ANY EXPERIENCE TO TRADE ONLINE,WE WILL DO IT ALL FOR YOU AND YOU WILL START EARNING A LIVING FROM TRADING ONLINE TODAY AND PROFITS WILL BE PAID TO YOUR ACCOUNT DIRECTLY. CLICK HERE TO REGISTER AND EARN